query:
SELECT se.id, se.eventoId, se.formandoId, se.tipoServico, se.quantidade, f.nome as formandoNome, e.tipoEvento
FROM servicos_execucao se 
JOIN formandos f ON se.formandoId = f.id 
JOIN eventos e ON se.eventoId = e.id
WHERE se.tipoServico LIKE '%cabelo%'
ORDER BY se.id DESC
LIMIT 20
